<span class="line"><span style="color:#F8F8F2;">transport.tcp.port: </span><span style="color:#BD93F9;">9300</span><span style="color:#F8F8F2;"> </span><span style="color:#6272A4;">#设置节点之间通信的tcp端口，默认是9300</span></span>
